I just wanted to ask because
obviously the scenarios

00:29:19.640 --> 00:29:23.570
that you are touching on--

00:29:23.570 --> 00:29:26.570
cancer, losing a child,
something like that--

00:29:26.570 --> 00:29:29.450
what if that is the
present and that's--

00:29:29.450 --> 00:29:33.005
we're focusing on the present
